The paper focuses on designing efficient neural networks for image classification, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The use of hyper-parameter optimization and Bayesian optimization suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The energy constraints and optimization also suggest a focus on neural engineering (cs.NE) and systems and control (cs.SY).
